column2: so good. I love when I find a unique breakfast spot
column4: let's face it...breakfast is so repetitive. Bacon
column6: waffles and pancakes. You really can't switch it up a whole lot from that. Here I was able to have an egg white scramble with cheese
column7: spinach and ARTICHOKES. Yes...this tasted like that awesome Artichoke pizza you can only get in New York but healthier and way more delicious.
